metadata.name: TOB #1
metadata.description: The Oddlings Bunch is an animated mashup of (The Abominable Bunch & Oddlings Game Club) two community-and-games orientated NFT projects, the very first of it's kind. Taking traits from each others collection the 3500 Unique NFTs in The Oddlings Bunch pay homage to both projects while carrying mysterious artifacts that can be chained/fused into one another once collected. Their purpose- a mystery.
